    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3400930/extras/a0f23424a7f47f43c99378d198bafbcc.avif?t=1771251006\" width=622 height=79 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《袜罪并罚！》中，你将与朋友们展开一场法庭混战！检察官抛出离谱指控，而你将运用证据卡牌捍卫自己，或者把被告怼得哑口无言。法官？只能在闹腾律师的咆哮中勉强维持秩序（通常以失败告终）。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3400930/extras/ff9b2cc5fc2f762dba2ea1f72b388af2.poster.avif?t=1771251006\" width=750 height=398 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3400930/extras/ff9b2cc5fc2f762dba2ea1f72b388af2.webm?t=1771251006\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3400930/extras/ff9b2cc5fc2f762dba2ea1f72b388af2.mp4?t=1771251006\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3400930/extras/8df3800a3622aa75d69807a58b63300e.avif?t=1771251006\" width=622 height=79 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >想当辩护律师还是检察官？拿上你的证据卡牌，组成对你有利的故事链吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3400930/extras/6b953916e5da10d699856a0935d73995.avif?t=1771251006\" width=620 height=256 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >想打乱对手的节奏？抢话、扔纸团、嘲讽——只要能左右判决，干啥都行！在这里，混乱就是法则。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3400930/extras/724a5448aab762de55a58dcf137c1515.poster.avif?t=1771251006\" width=750 height=398 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3400930/extras/724a5448aab762de55a58dcf137c1515.webm?t=1771251006\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3400930/extras/724a5448aab762de55a58dcf137c1515.mp4?t=1771251006\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3400930/extras/db9985c31ac0b5e4be69334366b47fe0.avif?t=1771251006\" width=622 height=79 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作为法官，你掌控着法庭——授予发言权、惩罚捣乱的律师，还能否决任何你觉得可疑（或纯属荒谬）的证据。无论你是公正裁决还是任性妄为，一切尽在你手！正义会胜利吗？呃……希望不大。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3400930/extras/0aecbd642a808f50c3e9b1dd35a72dc2.poster.avif?t=1771251006\" width=750 height=398 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3400930/extras/0aecbd642a808f50c3e9b1dd35a72dc2.webm?t=1771251006\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3400930/extras/0aecbd642a808f50c3e9b1dd35a72dc2.mp4?t=1771251006\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3400930/extras/85bdb0b54198d4a6977ac27e8416ddc4.avif?t=1771251006\" width=622 height=79 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>证人</strong> – 通过提供关键事实支持控方或辩方，影响庭审局势。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>法警</strong> – 使用工具制服捣乱者，维持法庭秩序。 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>记者</strong> – 每场庭审最多可发布3条突发新闻，作为证据使用。 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>陪审员 </strong>– 通过按钮投票有罪与否，并在画板上涂鸦。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>被告/原告</strong> – 向其他玩家发送消息来影响他们，并为己方律师的陈述提供支持。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这些角色为每场庭审增添了混乱、策略与幽默！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3400930/extras/6a6f5d07aa3ddf97baebe45bd758bb40.poster.avif?t=1771251006\" width=800 height=424 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3400930/extras/6a6f5d07aa3ddf97baebe45bd758bb40.webm?t=1771251006\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3400930/extras/6a6f5d07aa3ddf97baebe45bd758bb40.mp4?t=1771251006\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>请注意：我们对玩家在游戏期间与陌生人分享的用户生成内容不承担责任。为获得最佳体验，建议与信赖的人一起游玩。</i></p>",
